{"ticker": "BFLY", "company": "BUTTERFLY NETWORK INC", "weight_sum": 2.07, "etfs": ["ARKG"], "is_private": false, "query": "($BFLY OR \"Butterfly Network\") -is:retweet min_faves:10 since:2026-04-29 until:2026-05-01", "n_fetched": 1, "n_kept": 1, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2049374885533650968", "url": "https://x.com/Berci/status/2049374885533650968", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/Berci/status/2049374885533650968", "text": "The CEO of Butterfly Network, that developes hand-held ultrasound devices, took his son to an emergency room after his pediatrician flagged a potential concern. They waited for three hours to get an ultrasound, which ruled out the doctor\u2019s worries.\n\n\u201c\ud835\udc3c\ud835\udc53 \ud835\udc61\u210e\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc61 \ud835\udc5d\ud835\udc52\ud835\udc51\ud835\udc56\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc61\ud835\udc5f\ud835\udc56\ud835\udc50\ud835\udc56\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc5b \u210e\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc51 \ud835\udc62\ud835\udc59\ud835\udc61\ud835\udc5f\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc60\ud835\udc5c\ud835\udc62\ud835\udc5b\ud835\udc51, \ud835\udc64\ud835\udc52 \ud835\udc64\ud835\udc5c\ud835\udc62\ud835\udc59\ud835\udc51\ud835\udc5b\u2019\ud835\udc61 \u210e\ud835\udc4e\ud835\udc63\ud835\udc52 \ud835\udc52\ud835\udc63\ud835\udc52\ud835\udc5b \ud835\udc54\ud835\udc5c\ud835\udc5b\ud835\udc52.\u201d\u00a0\n\nThis is actually a good story and example for bringing affordable, AI-driven ultrasound devices to primary care.\n\nI tested their device a few years ago. Now it costs around 4000 USD compared to other devices starting at 30.000 USD. And AI analysis is built in.\n\nIt could mean that the trajectory for hand-held, smartphone-connected ultrasound is for every primary care physician to have one. If they have no prior training, the AI would guide them through the process. \n\nIt's not a far-fetched vision anymore.\n\nSource: https://t.co/j4cSMrR3dc", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 6, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 13, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 1120, "createdAt": "Wed Apr 29 06:27:02 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 4, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2049374885533650968", "displayTextRange": [0, 258], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "Berci", "url": "https://x.com/Berci", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/Berci", "id": "1940581", "name": "Berci Mesk\u00f3, MD, PhD", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1519553395488657408/XA0TIUv0_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1940581/1772714980", "description": "", "location": "Budapest, Hungary", "followers": 76575, "following": 93, "status": "", "canDm": false, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Thu Mar 22 21:38:21 +0000 2007", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 1047, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 18163, "statusesCount": 71864, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["1866062702424039918"], "profile_bio": {"description": "The Medical Futurist, Author of \"Your Map to the Future\", Global Keynote Speaker, and Futurist Researcher", "entities": {"description": {}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "medicalfuturist.com", "expanded_url": "http://medicalfuturist.com", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/JxsBimVkoL"}]}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {"media": [{"display_url": "pic.twitter.com/rtMryupa1O", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/Berci/status/2049374885533650968/photo/1", "ext_media_availability": {"status": "Available"}, "features": {"large": {"faces": [{"h": 102, "w": 102, "x": 486, "y": 54}]}, "orig": {"faces": [{"h": 102, "w": 102, "x": 486, "y": 54}]}}, "id_str": "2049374881221943296", "indices": [259, 282], "media_ke